 that other people have done, work we have done,

09:20.060 --> 09:21.900
 also compared it with animal models,

09:21.900 --> 09:23.380
 like those who can imitate sounds,

09:23.380 --> 09:25.580
 like parrots and songbirds,

09:25.580 --> 09:29.580
 I start to see there really isn't such a sharp distinction.

