 we humans become deaf, our speech starts to deteriorate

23:37.480 --> 23:39.040
 without any kind of therapy.

23:40.000 --> 23:45.000
 If a non-human primate or let's say a chicken becomes deaf,

23:46.520 --> 23:50.400
 their vocalizations don't deteriorate, very little at least.

